{
  "stem": "17299.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could cook with wood, and same time it would heat the other room also.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was an outhouse for sanitary--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--purpose, and there was running water on the outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a big stable was full with firewood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were no rations whatsoever because we had our-- the knapsacks that we brought in from Germany, we were eating from that--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and what we found in the house-- what the Jews or the people who left there before left behind.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German only.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First, we had to unload ships for the German army under supervision of soldiers, which were driving us for the first two or three days.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then, my oldest brother and my younger brother, myself, and a couple of other fellows too, were taken into the food depot, and we had to count cases and bags to be ready-- get them ready to be loaded into boxcars.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the work had to be done by Russian POWs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Germans told us stay away from the Russians, because they have body lice.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Otherwise, you will be eaten alive by the lice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When we saw the Russian POWs we got a shock, because they were walking skeletons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the same warehouse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were walking skeletons, and the Germans were beating them with rubber truncheons and-- to drive them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we saw the Russians stealing some food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, we saw they were undernourished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yes, we could understand, but we couldn't understand why were they were undernourished and what was going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, we were marched forth and back to the ghetto every day, but we did not get any food from the Germans for the first four days.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then on the fifth day we got some soup from the army at noontime.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
